cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.SY, cs.PL

Reasoning: 
1. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper explicitly mentions the problem of control synthesis for multi-agent systems and discusses a strategy synthesis problem for the whole team. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper deals with the synthesis of strategies to achieve complex, high-level, long-term goals. 
3. cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses linear temporal logic formula to specify the task requirements and constraints. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with control synthesis for multi-agent systems. 
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper discusses an iterative algorithm for solving short horizon planning problems.
